# Unsolved — Environment Variables
#
# This project has NO required environment variables. It runs entirely client
# side and uses CARTO's keyless basemap tiles, so it works out of the box with
# no secrets or API keys to configure.
#
# The single OPTIONAL override below lets you swap in a different map tile
# provider (for example, a keyed Stadia Maps or MapTiler style). If you set it,
# remember that Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_ to the browser —
# and that anything exposed to the browser is PUBLIC, so never put a true secret
# here. Use a referer-restricted tile key if your provider requires one.

# Optional: custom XYZ tile URL template (defaults to CARTO light_all if unset).
# VITE_MAP_TILE_URL="https://{s}.basemaps.cartocdn.com/light_all/{z}/{x}/{y}{r}.png"
